I like to put the Katakana Transliteration into 500 weighted Noto Serif JP with this code: 
                                                                                                /* Target all elements with lang="ja" */
                                                                                                  [lang="ja"] {
                                                                                                      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; /* Japanese Font */
                                                                                                      font-weight: 500; /* Set font weight to 500 */
                                                                                                  }
